events.name: 後半ごろつき排除依頼　勝利

parameters: スラムごろつき　戦闘

\n< Serena >Geez, there's no end to them, whether they come
out of the ground or pop up from a hole. Dealing
with these kinds of people is such a hassle.

\n< Serena >I suppose you could say it's convenient for me if
you think of it as helping with my work...
\n< Serena >Well, fine. Let's go back and finish the report.

\n< Serena >So you're saying I let my guard down against these
kind of people... Winning just makes me even more
disgusted...

\n< Serena >...There's no longer any use... Let's go back and
report.

image.characterName: エネミー BT_チンピラ04-1

events.name: 前半ごろつき排除依頼　勝利

parameters: スラムごろつき　戦闘

\n< Serena >However, shouldn't the local police be the ones
dealing with these kinds of people?

\n< Serena >With the increase in requests to adventurers, I
might be able to be happy in my position... but
it's a bit of a complicated feeling.
\n< Serena >Well... let's go back and finish the report.
